title: Harlequin Blaze - December 2014 [epub]
description:
[b]Publication Date: December 1, 2014[/b]

Harlequin Blaze brings you four new red-hot reads for one great price, available now! This Harlequin Blaze bundle includes A Last Chance Christmas by NEW YORK TIMES bestselling author Vicki Lewis Thompson, Bring Me to Life by Kira Sinclair, Wild Holiday Nights by Samantha Hunter, Meg Maguire and Debbi Rawlins and Under the Mistletoe by USA TODAY bestselling author Katherine Garbera.

Look for four new sexy, steamy stories every month from Harlequin Blaze!
